---
import I18n from './I18n.astro';
import QuickFacts from './QuickFacts.astro';
---

<section class="hero reveal">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <div class="hero-tag">
      <I18n
        en="Java architect · 14 years in"
        zh="Java 架构师 · 十四年"
      />
    </div>
    <h1>
      <I18n en="Fourteen years as a " zh="十四年" />
      <span class="accent">
        <I18n en="programmer." zh="程序员。" />
      </span>
      <I18n
        en=" Microservices, data warehouses, teams I've led."
        zh=" 微服务、数仓，也带过团队。"
      />
    </h1>
    <p>
      <I18n
        en="Mostly internet backends—mobile apps, management systems, and SaaS—with platform and team lead roles along the way. Lately: internal architecture, legacy refactors, and breaking monoliths into services."
        zh="主要在互联网企业做过后端和平台负责人——APP、各类管理系统与企业 SaaS 都写过。最近几年做内部系统架构、老项目重构，以及微服务拆分。"
      />
    </p>
  </div>
  <QuickFacts />
</section>
